						<summary>

						<p>Fragment near the Jod-Īśvara temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">12th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>The slab is broken on all sides. It seems to record a gift of land probably to a temple. It is in characters of about the 12th century A.D.</p>						

